import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Button, Grid, Card, CardContent, TextField } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <HeroSection />
      <Container sx={{ py: 8 }}>
        {/* About Us */}
        <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 8 }}>
          <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom color="text.primary">
            Who We Are
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" sx={{ maxWidth: '800px', mx: 'auto' }}>
            Hono Technology is a leader in IT innovation, delivering tailored solutions that drive growth. Our partnership with Zvertex AI empowers us to provide cutting-edge tools for businesses and professionals alike.
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        {/* Services */}
        <Box sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
          <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom align="center" color="text.primary">
            Our Expertise
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={4}>
            {[
              { title: 'App Development', desc: 'Custom mobile and web apps.' },
              { title: 'Data Engineering', desc: 'Insightful data solutions.' },
              { title: 'IT Consulting', desc: 'Strategic IT guidance.' },
              { title: 'Cloud Computing', desc: 'Scalable cloud infrastructure.' },
            ].map((service) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={service.title}>
                <Card>
                  <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">{service.title}</Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">{service.desc}</Typography>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Box>

        {/* Testimonials */}
        <Box sx={{ mb: 8, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom color="text.primary">
            What Our Clients Say
          </Typography>
          <Card sx={{ maxWidth: '600px', mx: 'auto', p: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" sx={{ fontStyle: 'italic' }}>
              "Hono Technology elevated our operations with their expertise and innovative approach."
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="primary" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              - Sarah Lee, CTO
            </Typography>
          </Card>
        </Box>

        {/* Consulting Pitch */}
        <Box
          sx={{
            bgcolor: 'success.main',
            color: 'white',
            py: 8,
            textAlign: 'center',
            borderRadius: 3,
            boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
          }}
        >
          <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom>
            Your Trusted IT Partner
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ mb: 4, fontWeight: 300 }}>
            Unleash your potential with our expert consulting services.
          </Typography>
          <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" component={Link} to="/contact" size="large">
            Let’s Collaborate
          </Button>
        </Box>

        {/* Newsletter */}
        <Box sx={{ mt: 8, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom color="text.primary">
            Stay Informed
          </Typography>
          <Box component="form" sx={{ maxWidth: '500px', mx: 'auto' }}>
            <TextField
              label="Enter your email"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              sx={{ mb: 3, bgcolor: 'white' }}
            />
            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" size="large">
              Subscribe Now
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Box>
      </Container>
      <ContactForm />
    </>
  );
};

export default Home;
